    {
      "id": "PopularPost335085",
      "post_content": "This is to [Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell) as [Searing Spear](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Searing Spear) is to [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt).   \n  \nI feel like this would be fairly costed at ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) for this effect. At ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) this really should have some upside, like [Dissipate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dissipate), [Spell Crumple](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Crumple)/[Hinder](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hinder), [Stoic Rebuttal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stoic Rebuttal), or [Forbid](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Forbid). As it is though, Cancel is just frustratingly underpowered.",
      "posted_by": "troll_berserker",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost335085\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">This is to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Counterspell\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell\">Counterspell</a> as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Searing Spear\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Searing Spear\">Searing Spear</a> is to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a>. <br/><br/>I feel like this would be fairly costed at <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/> for this effect. At <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/> this really should have some upside, like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dissipate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dissipate\">Dissipate</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spell Crumple\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Crumple\">Spell Crumple</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hinder\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hinder\">Hinder</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stoic Rebuttal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stoic Rebuttal\">Stoic Rebuttal</a>, or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Forbid\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Forbid\">Forbid</a>. As it is though, Cancel is just frustratingly underpowered.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '335085'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy99862\">troll_berserker</span>\r\n                                (8/14/2013 9:00:21 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>